These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-5-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, australian
There are 2 different favourite colors: aquamarine, mauve
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, swimming
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking
1. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
4. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the right of the australian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite      | hot-chocolate |
| Flower          | amaryllis    | dahlia     |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese        |
| Color           | mauve       | aquamarine      |
| Sport         | swimming    | golf          |
| Hobby     | filmmaking  | camping       |

