.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-5-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, water
House: wooden, palace
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, amber
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, american
2 different pets are kept: frog, turtle
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, adventure
1. the palace house is the person who likes amber##1
2. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
3. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
4. the wooden house is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | water       | coffee     |
| House         | palace | wooden |
| Color           | amber    | azure     |
| Nationality   | american        | canadian        |
| Pet           | turtle      | frog       |
| Movie-Genre         | spy     | adventure |

